---
title: Ultimate Veggie Bánh Mì Inspired Sub with Meat-Free Balls, Handcut Chips, Sriracha Mayo and Zingy Lime Slaw
description: Looking for a taste of everyday luxury? This Ultimate Veggie Bánh Mì Inspired Sub is our best ever version, with premium ingredients for an extra special vegetarian twist on a classic recipe. Bánh mì demonstrates the strong influence of France on Vietnamese cuisine, recognisable through ingredients such as baguettes and pâté.
